&lt;p&gt;Iranian President Masoud Pezeshkian was welcomed at the Prime Minister House in Islamabad with a guard of honour, as he paid a brief visit to Pakistan on Tuesday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pezeshkian is on an official visit to Pakistan at Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif’s invitation.&lt;/p&gt;
